Two Souls In Sync '26 premium wedding website

To preview:
1. Unzip the folder.
2. Open index.html.

To publish on Netlify:
1. Sign in to Netlify.
2. Drag the unzipped folder into the deploy area.
3. Netlify will create a public link.
4. You can rename the site in Site configuration.

Included:
- Opening invitation screen
- Background music with play/pause button
- Animated flower petals
- Rotating hero photos
- Countdown
- Love story
- Wedding details
- Google Maps button
- Add-to-calendar file
- Gallery lightbox
- WhatsApp RSVP
- Mobile layout
